page.title: 15Louise Stitt - Schoolgirl.
page.content: This is a typical day for me here in Stifford Clays. 5.50am.Out of bed, brush my teeth-I hate to swim with dirty teeth. 6.00am.To the pool,my coach arrives, the hard work begins.Afterwards-home for breakfast of cereals. 8.30am.Mum gives me a lift to school. 3.15pm.End of school-home get changed for dancing lessons.In September we are doing our 'Silver' test. 5.45pm.Dinner.After I watch 'Fame' I just love all the dancing and singing. 8.00pm.Swimming again.You have to work really hard when your in the 'A'squad at Thurrock Swimming Club.The session finishes with a shampoo fight in the showers. 10.15pm.Dad picks me up from Blackshotts Pool and, after an action packed day I collapse into bed. Louise Stitt.
